text: I can see some people not liking this one due to the high pitched sounds, they can definitely annoy some sensitive ears especially when you have headphones on. Strangely enough, I still think listening to this track with headphones is the way to go to get lost into its spacey mood. High pitched noises and a structure that sometimes feels all over the place, yet one of my favorites in the series. I'll be happy to play some Katamari on my Switch!
